West Street, Franklin to North Moore Street. (Before Reconstruction).
June 9, 1918.

West Street, at, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner of Franklin Street. Also shown is Franklin Street, south side, east from West, to and including Greenwich Streets.

August 4, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.
